body:
## Steps to reproduce the issue

I have a minimal blinky design to test CXXRTL VCD wave dumping:

[blink_vcd.tar.gz](https://github.com/YosysHQ/yosys/files/4750256/blink_vcd.tar.gz)

I run `make`.

## Expected behavior

It compiles.

## Actual behavior

Both g++ and clang++ fail to compile `cxxrtl_vcd_capi.cc`.

clang++: 
```
/home/tom/tools/yosys/backends/cxxrtl/cxxrtl_vcd_capi.cc:47:24: error: use of undeclared identifier 'debug_item'
        vcd->writer.add(name, debug_item(*object));
                              ^
/home/tom/tools/yosys/backends/cxxrtl/cxxrtl_vcd_capi.cc:58:38: error: unknown type name 'debug_item'; did you mean 'cxxrtl::debug_item'?
